created: 2022-09-30, last updated: 2026-06-12, [Read more](https://www.apideck.com/file-storage-api/upload-sessions)

# File Storage Upload Sessions API
One unified API to sync upload sessions across all major file storage platforms.
Build once, integrate everywhere.
...
Standard CRUD operations normalized across all platforms
ListGET
`/upload-sessions`
Retrieve all upload sessions with pagination and filtering
GetGET
`/upload-sessions/{id}`
Fetch a single upload session by ID
CreatePOST
`/upload-sessions`
Create a new upload session
UpdatePATCH
`/upload-sessions/{id}`
Update an existing upload session
## Quick Start
...
```
import { Apideck } from '@apideck/node'
const apideck = new Apideck({
apiKey: 'YOUR_API_KEY',
appId: 'YOUR_APP_ID',
consumerId: 'user-123'
})
// List upload sessions from any connected file storage platform
const response = await apideck.file-storage.uploadsessionsAll()
// Returns normalized data regardless of the underlying platform
console.log(response.data)
// [
// { id: '123', ...
},
// { id: '456', ...
}
// ]
// Works the same for Xero, QuickBooks, NetSuite, etc.
